OL,3,CMan caught on CCTV riding moped into
OL,4,CJD Sports
OL,6,FCCTV footage captured the moped bring
OL,7,Fdriven into a JD Sports shop in
OL,8,FNewcastle
OL,10,FA man who rode a moped down the
OL,11,Fpavements of a busy Newcastle shopping
OL,12,Fstreet before going inside a store has
OL,13,Fbeen put behind bars.
OL,15,FKavan Conroy was caught on CCTV riding
OL,16,Fdown pedestrian pavements on
OL,17,FNorthumberland Street and Blackett
OL,18,FStreet on the moped before going into
OL,19,FJD Sports.
