OL,3,CMan caught on CCTV riding moped into
OL,4,CJD Sports
OL,6,FConroy, 21, had no helmet on and no
OL,7,Flicence plate on the moped at the time.
OL,9,FFollowing the incident on 21 March, as
OL,10,Fofficers pledge to continue to crack
OL,11,Fdown on city centre crime, Northumbria
OL,12,FPolice launched an investigation into
OL,13,FConroy, with a trawl of CCTV
OL,14,Fidentifying him.
OL,16,FAfter verbally abusing two police
OL,17,Fofficers at Eldon Square, the
OL,18,Foffender, who has previous convictions
OL,19,Ffor theft and criminal damage, kicked
OL,20,Fan officer in the face while he was in
OL,21,Fa police van.
