OL,3,CMan caught on CCTV riding moped into
OL,4,CJD Sports
OL,6,FConroy, of no fixed abode, pleaded
OL,7,Fguilty to dangerous driving,
OL,8,Fthreatening behaviour, having no
OL,9,Finsurance, driving otherwise than in
OL,10,Faccordance with a licence and
OL,11,Fassaulting an emergency worker.
OL,13,FAt Newcastle Crown Court on Friday 10
OL,14,FMay, he was jailed for 11 months and
OL,15,Falso banned from driving.
