OL,6,FFollowing Conroy's sentencing, area
OL,7,Fcommander for Newcastle, Chief
OL,8,FSuperintendent Barrie Joisce, of
OL,9,FNorthumbria Police, said: "Conroy's
OL,10,Factions were disgraceful on the day he
OL,11,Fcarried out these offences and he is
OL,12,Fnow rightly behind bars.
OL,14,F"He showed a complete disregard for
OL,15,Fthe safety and welfare of others by
OL,16,Friding a moped down a pedestrian area
OL,17,Fbefore going on to assault one our
OL,18,Fofficers.
