OL,6,F"It was extremely fortunate that
OL,7,Fsomeone was not seriously injured by
OL,8,FConroy and he now has time in prison
OL,9,Fto reflect on his actions."
OL,11,FConroy's sentencing comes after the
OL,12,Flaunch of the Newcastle City Safe
OL,13,Fpartnership earlier this month.
OL,15,FBased at the City Library site, the
OL,16,Fnew multi-agency initiative sees
OL,17,FNorthumbria Police, NE1 and Newcastle
OL,18,FCity Council working together to make
OL,19,FNewcastle an even better place to
OL,20,Flive, work and visit.
